<para id="RM000000W6Z027X" category="D" type-id="3001B" name-id="AT02X-73" from="200601">
<name>HOW TO PROCEED WITH TROUBLESHOOTING</name>
<subpara id="RM000000W6Z027X_z0" proc-id="RM0250U___00005XF00000">
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<atten4>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>The ECM of this system is connected to the CAN and multiplex communication system. Therefore, before starting troubleshooting, make sure to check that there is no trouble in the CAN and multiplex communication systems.</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>The intelligent tester can be used at steps 3, 4, 6, and 9.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
